---

<section id="feed" class="bg-dark px-4 py-20 border-t border-gold/10">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4 text-white">
      AI 前沿<span class="text-gold">周报</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-gold mx-auto mb-16"></div>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <!-- 周报项 1 -->
      <article class="group p-6 border-l-2 border-gold/30 hover:border-gold transition-colors hover:bg-dark/50">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white group-hover:text-gold transition-colors">
            智能体基建元年：四大巨头同时出手
          </h3>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 whitespace-nowrap ml-4">2026年4月7日</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">
          Google AutoBNN 强化预测、OpenAI Codex 搞定代码生成、Anthropic Claude 4 定义安全边界、Microsoft Azure AI Agent Service 正式商用。基础设施已铺好，应用层窗口期正在打开。
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href="https://blog.research.google/2024/03/autobnn-probabilistic-time-series.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-gold text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">Google →</a>
          <a href="https://openai.com/index/gpt-5-3" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-gold text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">OpenAI →</a>
          <a href="https://anthropic.com/claude-4" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-gold text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">Anthropic →</a>
          <a href="https://azure.microsoft.com/ai-agents" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-gold text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">Microsoft →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- 周报项 2 -->
      <article class="group p-6 border-l-2 border-gold/30 hover:border-gold transition-colors hover:bg-dark/50">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white group-hover:text-gold transition-colors">
            AI 正在阉割谁的技能？Anthropic 实验揭示的真相
          </h3>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 whitespace-nowrap ml-4">2026年4月3日</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">
          Anthropic 研究发现：使用 AI 编程的开发者理解测试得分低 17%。"认知卸载"会阻碍技能形成，但"认知辅助"不会。关键在于你是让 AI 代写，还是追问为什么。
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/research/AI-assistance-coding-skills" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-gold text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">原文 →</a>
          <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.20245" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-gold text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">arXiv →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- 周报项 3 -->
      <article class="group p-6 border-l-2 border-gold/30 hover:border-gold transition-colors hover:bg-dark/50">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white group-hover:text-gold transition-colors">
            模型战争白热化：GPT-5.4、Claude 4.6、Gemini 3 同台竞技
          </h3>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 whitespace-nowrap ml-4">2026年3月17日</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">
          四大巨头两周内密集发布旗舰模型。OpenAI 推出 Pro 和 Thinking 双版本，Anthropic 战略转向知识工作，Google 原生多模态架构。DeepSeek V4 开源挑战者备受期待。
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href="https://deepmind.google/models/gemini/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-gold text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">Gemini →</a>
          <a href="https://ai2.work/blog/deepseek-v4-china-s-trillion-parameter-multimodal-ai-rival-in-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-gold text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">DeepSeek →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- 周报项 4 -->
      <article class="group p-6 border-l-2 border-gold/30 hover:border-gold transition-colors hover:bg-dark/50">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white group-hover:text-gold transition-colors">
            本地 LLM 战略：一人公司的算力突围
          </h3>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 whitespace-nowrap ml-4">进行中</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">
          基于 M5 Pro 工作台的实测对比，探讨本地部署 vs API 调用的成本与性能权衡。数据隐私、长期成本、任务场景——做出最优选择的关键考量。
        </p>
        <a href="/briefings" class="text-gold text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">更多详情 →</a>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <a href="/briefings" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 border-2 border-gold text-gold hover:bg-gold hover:text-dark transition-all font-semibold">
        查看全部周报
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
